669
00:51:35,260 --> 00:51:36,220
HORIZONTE PARALELO

670
00:51:36,300 --> 00:51:37,820
Abaixar protetor da face!

671
00:51:39,180 --> 00:51:41,060
Ó, Cristo.

672
00:51:41,100 --> 00:51:42,620
Saiam já daí!

673
00:51:42,700 --> 00:51:44,460
HORIZONTE PARALELO

