679
00:52:57,380 --> 00:53:00,180
Mark, Mikhail, saiam já daí!

680
00:53:20,260 --> 00:53:21,340
Acionar propulsores.

681
00:53:21,420 --> 00:53:23,620
- Portas de carga abertas.
